originalText.text: Highly recommended. Prompt response time on any inquiries. Only wish 50/50 was allowed on win4 and also combo numbers on both numbers & win4. A little challenging when you win over $600. Other than that its an awesome app. So convenient.

originalText.text: It's very convenient. When I'm crushed with time and can't make it to the local store,I can just pull out my phone and put all my numbers in instantly. I'll get a notification with a photo of my lottery tickets and when I win I get a email and I can check my Jackpocket account and my money is there.I do love to play at the local store, but I love having the option to play right from home or anywhere within my state. Now I do see some advertisement for something called Jackpot don't be fooled they are not the original Jackpocket come join me you'll enjoy it too. Very safe very convenient.
